WEBVTT

00:11.080 --> 00:11.880
What happened?

00:11.550 --> 00:18.180
[1995]

00:11.880 --> 00:13.160
Just look at what you've done to my son!

00:13.160 --> 00:13.830
Apologize!

00:13.830 --> 00:14.930
-You must apologize!
-Brother is there.

00:14.930 --> 00:15.590
Okay, okay.

00:16.710 --> 00:18.000
Sir! Sir!

00:18.570 --> 00:19.800
Don't get physical.
Let's talk this through.

00:19.800 --> 00:21.510
Adults shouldn't bully children!

00:21.510 --> 00:23.440
Look how badly he's beaten my son!

00:23.470 --> 00:24.400
Everyone, look!

00:24.670 --> 00:25.390
What's wrong with saying that?

00:25.390 --> 00:26.440
Isn't that the truth?

00:26.440 --> 00:27.510
You were born but not properly raised!

00:27.510 --> 00:28.830
Look how viciously you beat him!

00:28.830 --> 00:30.290
Alright, let's calm down.

00:30.430 --> 00:32.020
We'll cover the medical bills.

00:32.020 --> 00:34.000
Let's try to talk this through, okay?

00:34.000 --> 00:35.540
If Jiang Cheng doesn't kneel down
and apologize today,

00:35.540 --> 00:36.440
this isn't over!

00:36.440 --> 00:37.080
Not over!

00:37.100 --> 00:38.360
So what if you're a cop?

00:38.450 --> 00:39.600
Come on.

00:40.070 --> 00:41.320
I am a cop, yes,

00:41.510 --> 00:43.300
but I am also his father!

00:43.560 --> 00:44.350
From today on,

00:44.350 --> 00:45.550
Jiang Cheng is my son!

00:45.600 --> 00:48.060
None of you shall say
he has no parents again!

00:56.470 --> 00:59.870
[Young Jiang Cheng]

01:08.400 --> 01:08.950
Brother!

01:08.980 --> 01:09.800
Let's make a toast!

01:09.800 --> 01:11.060
Sure, sister. Come on.

01:11.060 --> 01:12.220
Me too! Me too!

01:12.600 --> 01:13.060
Come on.

01:13.080 --> 01:13.800
Cheers!

01:19.400 --> 01:20.150
Brother!

01:21.220 --> 01:21.680
Come on.

01:23.730 --> 01:24.340
Brother,

01:24.370 --> 01:25.570
me too!

01:26.350 --> 01:26.810
Come on.

01:27.070 --> 01:28.400
Brother, lift me up too.

01:29.970 --> 01:30.560
Brother!

01:30.910 --> 01:31.510
Brother!

01:32.140 --> 01:32.600
Come on!

01:33.479 --> 01:34.810
You need to lose weight.

01:35.780 --> 01:36.979
He's my brother.

01:37.090 --> 01:38.690
Your brother is my brother.

01:39.220 --> 01:40.700
No, he's mine alone!

01:40.789 --> 01:41.560
Stingy.

01:41.920 --> 01:42.350
Chuan,

01:42.570 --> 01:43.850
let's become sworn siblings.

01:43.850 --> 01:44.280
Sure.

01:44.300 --> 01:45.460
You're the eldest.

01:45.680 --> 01:46.590
I'm second,

01:47.170 --> 01:48.170
Zhan Wei third,

01:48.320 --> 01:49.320
Yan Bin fourth,

01:50.229 --> 01:51.570
and that makes you fifth.

01:51.570 --> 01:52.050
No,

01:52.120 --> 01:53.450
I don't want to be fifth.

01:53.509 --> 01:54.890
-You're fifth!
-Fifth!

01:54.920 --> 02:00.850
-Fifth!
-Fifth!

03:23.320 --> 03:29.000
[Sunsets Secrets Regrets]

03:29.320 --> 03:31.820
[Episode 12]

03:34.180 --> 03:35.010
Hansheng.

03:42.870 --> 03:44.360
Gifts should be returned in kind.

03:44.360 --> 03:45.990
Congratulations on graduating from
the Public Security University.

03:45.990 --> 03:47.220
Come visit whenever you can.

03:47.220 --> 03:48.350
I'll buy you a drink.

03:51.030 --> 03:51.560
Take it.

03:56.140 --> 03:56.770
Thank you.

04:02.620 --> 04:03.550
Jiang Hansheng.

04:58.930 --> 04:59.970
Turns out,

05:00.210 --> 05:04.020
if you want to
get under Officer Jiang's skin,

05:04.050 --> 05:06.930
all it takes is the right girl.

05:07.450 --> 05:09.120
Are you scared,

05:10.010 --> 05:11.240
Officer Jiang?

05:15.630 --> 05:17.270
Hansheng, are you alright?

05:27.680 --> 05:28.480
Let's get out.

05:31.270 --> 05:32.470
There's another way.

05:34.800 --> 05:35.800
What way?

05:39.310 --> 05:42.120
During those six days at the warehouse
in the 8/17 Case,

05:42.120 --> 05:43.480
there might be some hidden information

05:43.480 --> 05:44.750
that I missed.

05:47.120 --> 05:48.090
I want to try.

05:49.070 --> 05:49.800
How?

05:53.360 --> 05:53.960
Hypnosis.

05:57.480 --> 05:59.340
What did you dream about just now?

06:02.190 --> 06:03.720
Just some bits of memories.

06:07.950 --> 06:09.080
So I was thinking...

06:10.750 --> 06:12.180
maybe hypnosis would work.

06:12.180 --> 06:13.630
Will that really work?

06:17.570 --> 06:19.330
I can't guarantee we'll find any clues.

06:19.330 --> 06:21.130
I'm not talking about the clues.

06:21.720 --> 06:22.750
I mean you.

06:25.570 --> 06:26.330
Can you

06:27.210 --> 06:28.410
really handle it?

06:39.510 --> 06:40.710
Don't push yourself.

06:44.680 --> 06:46.010
I'm not pushing myself.

06:47.390 --> 06:48.120
Zhou Jin,

06:49.670 --> 06:51.130
I want to try one more time.

07:12.870 --> 07:14.120
Around 2:00 AM this morning,

07:14.120 --> 07:15.290
the police emergency line
received a report:

07:15.290 --> 07:16.800
a silver-gray sedan

07:16.800 --> 07:17.870
suddenly caught fire,

07:17.870 --> 07:19.370
veered off the road,
and plunged into a river.

07:19.370 --> 07:20.270
The salvage team is currently

07:20.270 --> 07:21.600
searching for the vehicle at the scene.

07:21.600 --> 07:23.850
The cause of the accident is
under further investigation.

07:23.850 --> 07:25.170
What's there to watch?

07:28.000 --> 07:29.080
That car is mine.

07:29.890 --> 07:30.940
Your car?

07:31.720 --> 07:32.830
Don't you want to know

07:32.830 --> 07:34.159
who was in the car, Boss?

07:37.430 --> 07:38.690
I want an explanation.

07:39.670 --> 07:40.480
Your car,

07:41.990 --> 07:43.720
and you're asking me for an explanation?

07:43.720 --> 07:45.159
It's not like I burned it.

07:46.530 --> 07:47.200
You did it?

07:50.550 --> 07:52.480
Why did you have Xiao Mao follow me?

07:52.580 --> 07:53.310
Jiang Cheng,

07:53.659 --> 07:55.790
how dare you talk to our boss like that?

07:56.430 --> 07:57.290
Let him finish.

07:58.480 --> 07:59.040
Boss.

08:01.060 --> 08:03.010
I burned the car with Xiao Mao inside.

08:03.010 --> 08:04.210
I didn't want to do it.

08:05.190 --> 08:06.910
But if I don't assert my authority,

08:06.910 --> 08:09.280
how am I supposed to survive
in this line of work?

08:09.280 --> 08:09.970
Cheng,

08:10.920 --> 08:12.350
you need to be clearer.

08:12.860 --> 08:14.270
Otherwise, I won't even know
how to answer...

08:14.270 --> 08:15.160
Boss!

08:16.700 --> 08:18.090
Xiao Mao told me everything.

08:18.090 --> 08:19.790
You gave him half a million to follow me

08:19.790 --> 08:21.760
and report all my movements to you.

08:24.190 --> 08:26.320
What exactly are you suspecting me of?

08:43.520 --> 08:45.550
The work we do is high-risk.

08:46.670 --> 08:48.530
It's natural to be more cautious.

08:49.120 --> 08:50.120
Old Scorpion said

08:50.270 --> 08:52.530
he's coming to oversee things in person.

08:53.120 --> 08:54.000
If it were you,

08:55.030 --> 08:55.760
wouldn't you

08:56.000 --> 08:57.750
also be extremely careful?

08:59.790 --> 09:02.650
Put yourself in my shoes,
and you'll understand me.

09:02.670 --> 09:03.430
Besides,

09:03.920 --> 09:05.780
I'm not just keeping an eye on you.

09:07.430 --> 09:09.090
But I trained Xiao Mao myself.

09:09.100 --> 09:10.900
Didn't I lose Zhengtian too?

09:12.000 --> 09:13.720
Traitors like them

09:14.030 --> 09:15.200
deserve to die.

09:15.830 --> 09:16.830
Just think of it

09:17.440 --> 09:18.290
that way.

09:22.440 --> 09:23.200
Boss.

09:25.980 --> 09:27.000
I told you before,

09:27.020 --> 09:29.020
I don't like being falsely accused.

09:29.550 --> 09:31.510
I told you on the first day
I started working for you

09:31.510 --> 09:32.420
that I was a cop.

09:32.730 --> 09:34.030
And if that bothered you,

09:34.030 --> 09:35.690
you didn't have to bring me in.

09:39.440 --> 09:41.100
It has nothing to do with that.

09:41.240 --> 09:42.900
With everything you know now,

09:42.930 --> 09:44.530
if you really wanted me dead,

09:44.790 --> 09:46.450
would I still be sitting here?

09:49.150 --> 09:50.120
But Cheng...

09:52.120 --> 09:54.520
are you really not
hiding anything from me?

09:58.360 --> 09:58.910
Zhou Jin.

09:59.910 --> 10:01.240
That's her name, right?

10:06.880 --> 10:09.120
Women are trouble.

10:16.050 --> 10:17.650
Whoever lays a finger on her,

10:17.720 --> 10:18.780
I'll go after them.

10:20.240 --> 10:21.120
Jiang Cheng,

10:21.800 --> 10:23.130
do you have a death wish?

10:23.190 --> 10:23.980
I said,

10:24.190 --> 10:25.390
whoever lays a finger on her,

10:25.390 --> 10:26.450
I'll go after them.

10:26.560 --> 10:27.680
I mean what I say.

10:30.070 --> 10:30.790
Love.

10:31.410 --> 10:33.570
Now that is what true love looks like.

10:38.480 --> 10:39.360
Well, at this point,

10:39.360 --> 10:41.020
I've got nothing left to hide.

10:42.850 --> 10:44.570
Back then, she was the one
who had me hauled away naked

10:44.570 --> 10:46.370
by the Public Security Brigade.

10:46.370 --> 10:48.100
Do you know what that felt like?

10:48.600 --> 10:49.360
Even today,

10:49.360 --> 10:51.360
she still looks at me like I'm trash.

10:52.370 --> 10:53.080
Boss,

10:53.570 --> 10:55.200
when we're out here in this game,

10:55.200 --> 10:56.800
we can't just be after money.

10:57.120 --> 10:59.450
We've got to earn some respect too, right?

11:01.150 --> 11:02.200
So how do you plan

11:03.660 --> 11:04.940
to earn that respect?

11:09.150 --> 11:10.210
If I can't have her,

11:11.100 --> 11:12.360
I'll just destroy her.

11:13.670 --> 11:15.830
But I have to be the one to do it.

11:16.910 --> 11:17.970
As for anyone else,

11:18.720 --> 11:20.240
whoever lays a finger on her,

11:20.240 --> 11:21.300
I'll come for them.

11:26.440 --> 11:27.080
Alright.

11:27.870 --> 11:28.670
I hear you.

11:41.840 --> 11:42.770
Are you calm now?

11:47.150 --> 11:47.870
Boss,

11:48.750 --> 11:50.480
stop sending people to test me.

11:51.240 --> 11:52.100
I've really...

11:53.200 --> 11:54.400
been worn out lately.

11:57.080 --> 11:57.720
I know.

11:59.030 --> 12:00.490
You've worked hard enough

12:00.870 --> 12:02.330
setting up the new routes.

12:02.910 --> 12:03.630
Relax.

12:04.630 --> 12:07.030
Old Scorpion's already decided
when he's coming.

12:07.030 --> 12:08.030
Get ready.

12:42.080 --> 12:42.800
Leader Yao,

12:42.820 --> 12:44.100
what's so urgent?

12:44.360 --> 12:45.220
Close the door.

12:45.350 --> 12:45.880
Sit down.

12:56.520 --> 12:57.280
What is it?

13:09.630 --> 13:10.480
What is this?

13:10.910 --> 13:12.200
This is intelligence passed back

13:12.200 --> 13:13.600
by an undercover of mine.

13:14.870 --> 13:15.910
A cargo ship

13:15.510 --> 13:19.160
[Oct. 3—closing in at Jingang Wharf]

13:16.390 --> 13:17.550
will dock at Jingang Wharf

13:17.550 --> 13:19.080
on October 3rd.

13:19.720 --> 13:21.600
There'll be a large-scale drug deal.

13:21.600 --> 13:22.730
When the time comes,

13:22.870 --> 13:25.870
people from Hengyun Logistics
will pick up the goods.

13:26.910 --> 13:27.840
They have guns.

13:29.790 --> 13:31.100
Is this intel reliable?

13:31.100 --> 13:31.980
Very reliable.

13:34.720 --> 13:35.630
Tan.

13:37.510 --> 13:38.710
It's been five years.

13:40.840 --> 13:41.550
You have to help me.

13:41.550 --> 13:43.280
Come on, don't say it like that.

13:43.510 --> 13:44.310
Rest assured,

13:44.840 --> 13:46.370
I'll definitely go all out.

13:48.000 --> 13:50.080
With approval
from the Provincial Bureau leadership,

13:50.080 --> 13:52.240
I'm now going to fully disclose

13:52.240 --> 13:53.840
all classified information

13:54.550 --> 13:55.950
related to the 8/17 Case.

13:56.750 --> 13:57.480
Wait a sec.

14:01.910 --> 14:02.720
Go ahead.

14:04.030 --> 14:05.150
Five years ago,

14:05.910 --> 14:07.000
the reason I was able to locate

14:07.000 --> 14:09.930
the hideout of the criminal gang
behind the 8/17 Case

14:10.960 --> 14:13.090
was because of Jiang Hansheng's help.

14:15.080 --> 14:17.340
He'd identified one of them beforehand,

14:17.780 --> 14:19.240
and that person was Qi Yan.

14:20.040 --> 14:21.550
We provoked Qi Yan

14:21.870 --> 14:23.470
to make him give himself away.

14:23.470 --> 14:24.750
At that time, every intersection

14:24.750 --> 14:26.680
in Haizhou had checkpoints set up.

14:27.200 --> 14:28.800
The gang committed the crime

14:29.050 --> 14:30.650
and couldn't leave the city.

14:30.790 --> 14:31.550
So they stayed in

14:31.550 --> 14:33.750
an abandoned warehouse in the suburbs.

14:34.360 --> 14:36.550
I was the one who led the team
to carry out the arrest.

14:36.550 --> 14:38.350
The plan was to catch them alive,

14:38.450 --> 14:40.110
but those cornered criminals

14:40.110 --> 14:41.710
put up a desperate struggle.

14:41.750 --> 14:43.150
So during the firefight,

14:43.660 --> 14:45.630
four suspects were killed on the spot,

14:45.630 --> 14:46.920
including Qi Yan.

14:47.660 --> 14:51.910
[Sixth day
after Jiang Hansheng was captured]

14:51.520 --> 14:52.120
Jiang Hansheng,

14:52.120 --> 14:52.960
don't shoot!

14:52.960 --> 14:53.620
Don't move!

14:54.220 --> 14:55.290
I'm Yao Weihai!

14:55.480 --> 14:56.550
Look closely, I'm Yao Weihai!

14:56.550 --> 14:56.910
Don't move!

14:56.910 --> 14:58.120
Officer Jiang!

14:58.240 --> 14:59.360
The police are here.

14:59.360 --> 15:01.030
Let's listen to the police, okay?

15:01.030 --> 15:02.000
I surrender.

15:02.310 --> 15:03.610
I surrender, Officer Jiang!

15:03.610 --> 15:04.520
Jiang Hansheng!

15:04.520 --> 15:05.590
I'm Yao Weihai!

15:05.620 --> 15:06.440
Officer Jiang,

15:06.440 --> 15:07.200
don't do anything rash.

15:07.200 --> 15:08.000
We have the situation under control.

15:08.000 --> 15:09.390
Don't do anything rash!

15:09.390 --> 15:11.550
Look closely! I'm here. Don't be nervous!

15:11.550 --> 15:12.480
I'm Yao Weihai!

15:12.480 --> 15:14.080
I just want to give this back to you!

15:14.080 --> 15:14.960
Listen to the police!

15:14.960 --> 15:15.690
Jiang Hansheng!

15:15.690 --> 15:17.000
I really surrender!

15:17.030 --> 15:17.980
Don't get agitated!

15:17.980 --> 15:18.580
Calm down!

15:20.750 --> 15:22.270
I will kill you!

15:23.510 --> 15:24.510
Qi Yan!

15:24.870 --> 15:25.750
No!

15:36.930 --> 15:38.150
After that operation,

15:38.150 --> 15:40.280
we continued verifying the identities

15:40.280 --> 15:41.480
of the four deceased.

15:41.630 --> 15:44.600
We eventually identified
the real name of one of them:

15:44.600 --> 15:45.840
Feng He.

15:47.510 --> 15:48.740
He had a prior record—

15:49.840 --> 15:52.220
he'd served time
for illegal arms trafficking.

15:52.220 --> 15:53.420
By mapping out

15:53.450 --> 15:54.640
Feng He's network,

15:55.240 --> 15:57.840
we discovered he had close dealings

15:58.080 --> 15:59.390
with a broker named He Wen.

15:59.390 --> 16:01.390
According to Feng He's associates,

16:01.480 --> 16:03.440
He Wen could get his hands on goods

16:03.440 --> 16:05.150
that others couldn't get on the market—

16:05.150 --> 16:06.550
drugs, firearms,

16:06.910 --> 16:08.110
wild animals,

16:08.480 --> 16:09.540
and even children—

16:10.200 --> 16:12.200
available in
both large and small quantities.

16:12.200 --> 16:13.270
He Wen?

16:13.910 --> 16:14.440
Right.

16:14.600 --> 16:15.360
Go on.

16:20.550 --> 16:22.950
At the time,
we suspected that behind He Wen

16:23.200 --> 16:26.270
there was
an entire criminal trade network.

16:26.960 --> 16:28.320
So, in order to completely take down

16:28.320 --> 16:29.580
this crime syndicate,

16:30.410 --> 16:31.240
five years ago, we

16:31.240 --> 16:33.400
launched an undercover operation

16:33.430 --> 16:34.630
codenamed Cangfeng.

16:35.200 --> 16:37.510
At that time,
He Wen was serving a sentence

16:37.510 --> 16:39.360
at Guhua Prison for attempted murder.

16:39.360 --> 16:40.690
I took that opportunity

16:40.960 --> 16:42.820
to have Cangfeng get close to him.

16:42.960 --> 16:45.220
We thought we'd find clues very quickly.

16:46.480 --> 16:48.080
But who would've thought...

16:49.200 --> 16:51.440
the waters in Haizhou ran this deep?

16:53.470 --> 16:54.760
Once we stepped in,

16:55.640 --> 16:57.840
five years passed in the blink of an eye.

17:01.000 --> 17:01.670
This...

17:02.780 --> 17:04.970
is the intel Cangfeng sent back?

17:05.000 --> 17:05.690
Yes.

17:07.640 --> 17:10.550
After five years of
undercover investigation, Cangfeng

17:10.550 --> 17:12.680
has helped us gain a general understanding

17:12.680 --> 17:14.680
of the gang
that orchestrated the 8/17 gun robbery

17:14.680 --> 17:16.010
and police murder case.

17:16.400 --> 17:18.640
They all belong to a crime syndicate

17:18.770 --> 17:20.200
led by Old Scorpion.

17:22.680 --> 17:23.750
Old Scorpion's

17:24.000 --> 17:26.200
name, age, and appearance

17:26.400 --> 17:27.329
remain unknown.

17:27.880 --> 17:29.010
Since the 8/17 Case,

17:29.110 --> 17:30.510
he hasn't shown up again.

17:30.510 --> 17:32.640
He has many branches under his control

17:33.440 --> 17:35.100
operating in various places,

17:35.440 --> 17:37.040
primarily dealing in drugs.

17:38.160 --> 17:40.560
The person who controls the Haizhou market

17:41.640 --> 17:43.440
is He Wu, chairman

17:44.300 --> 17:45.560
of Hengyun Logistics.

17:46.350 --> 17:47.640
He Wen, He Wu...

17:48.720 --> 17:49.680
They're brothers?

17:49.680 --> 17:50.480
That's right.

17:51.680 --> 17:52.480
Old Scorpion,

17:53.990 --> 17:55.270
He Wen, He Wu,

17:55.640 --> 17:56.440
Feng He—

17:56.460 --> 17:59.320
they all belong to
the same criminal organization.

18:02.550 --> 18:04.030
If Old Scorpion shows up

18:05.110 --> 18:06.970
during the deal at Jingang Wharf,

18:08.440 --> 18:11.500
I'll have a chance
to wipe them all out in one fell swoop.

18:12.240 --> 18:12.880
Alright.

18:14.270 --> 18:15.030
Leader Yao,

18:15.640 --> 18:16.480
just tell me

18:18.070 --> 18:19.400
what you need me to do.

18:24.380 --> 18:25.010
Tan.

18:26.880 --> 18:28.310
I need you off-site,

18:29.390 --> 18:30.850
directing the operation.

18:32.160 --> 18:33.440
Because I have to personally lead the team

18:33.440 --> 18:34.970
to the wharf for the arrest.

18:35.510 --> 18:36.600
That won't do.

18:37.750 --> 18:39.000
You're the overall commander—

18:39.000 --> 18:40.110
the leader of the task force.

18:40.110 --> 18:42.070
How can you personally
carry out the arrest?

18:42.070 --> 18:43.070
Cangfeng

18:43.960 --> 18:45.070
is still inside.

18:46.630 --> 18:48.360
Only I can coordinate with him.

18:49.590 --> 18:50.960
I've already reported

18:51.510 --> 18:54.170
this final operation
to the Provincial Bureau.

18:55.240 --> 18:56.690
The city's SWAT team

18:56.720 --> 18:58.920
will serve as the main force in this raid

18:59.070 --> 19:00.930
and come with me to Jingang Wharf.

19:01.000 --> 19:02.130
The Nancheng Branch

19:02.310 --> 19:05.040
will also establish
a temporary command center.

19:05.120 --> 19:07.440
Leaders from the Provincial Bureau
will be present to oversee the operation.

19:07.440 --> 19:08.240
And you

19:08.910 --> 19:11.310
will take command of the entire operation,

19:11.310 --> 19:12.840
coordinating everything.

19:13.920 --> 19:14.590
Tan,

19:15.830 --> 19:16.960
I'm counting on you.

19:31.330 --> 19:36.830
[10:45 AM, October 3]

19:44.110 --> 19:44.880
Hurry up!

20:00.220 --> 20:00.940
Senior...

20:05.570 --> 20:06.280
Leaders,

20:06.370 --> 20:07.430
everything is ready upstairs.

20:07.430 --> 20:08.430
Let me show you in.

20:10.650 --> 20:11.650
Watch your steps.

20:25.640 --> 20:26.160
Dr. Su.

20:26.200 --> 20:27.030
Zhou.

20:27.820 --> 20:29.130
This is Professor Ding.

20:29.130 --> 20:30.260
This is Officer Zhou.

20:30.260 --> 20:30.900
Nice to meet you.

20:30.900 --> 20:31.830
Nice to meet you.

20:31.930 --> 20:33.590
She's Jiang Hansheng's wife.

20:33.680 --> 20:34.440
Really?

20:34.860 --> 20:35.930
We're ready.

20:36.020 --> 20:37.150
Please come with me.

20:41.410 --> 20:42.220
It's upstairs.

20:42.220 --> 20:42.590
Okay.

20:44.400 --> 20:45.000
Zhou,

20:45.540 --> 20:47.920
you guys are still so busy
during the holidays.

20:47.920 --> 20:49.510
Criminals don't take holidays either.

20:49.510 --> 20:50.240
True.

20:58.660 --> 20:59.260
This way.

20:59.280 --> 20:59.830
Okay.

21:11.870 --> 21:12.470
Chief Tan,

21:12.730 --> 21:13.850
we have full access to all CCTV feeds

21:13.850 --> 21:14.850
at Jingang Wharf.

21:14.890 --> 21:15.550
Keep a close watch on them.

21:15.550 --> 21:16.110
Yes, sir.

21:23.960 --> 21:26.290
All units, report your status in real time

21:26.880 --> 21:28.330
once you reach your designated positions.

21:28.330 --> 21:29.460
Respond if you copy.

21:29.830 --> 21:30.590
Team A, copy.

21:31.070 --> 21:31.830
Team B, copy.

21:32.540 --> 21:33.300
Team C, copy.

21:38.550 --> 21:40.000
How's it going on He Wu's side?

21:40.000 --> 21:40.730
He just left.

21:40.740 --> 21:41.870
Wan is tailing him.

21:53.940 --> 21:54.980
You can lie down.

21:55.510 --> 21:57.880
Make yourself as comfortable as possible.

21:57.880 --> 21:58.680
Lie down.

22:06.310 --> 22:07.240
Jiang Hansheng.

22:08.570 --> 22:09.760
Are you sure...

22:11.310 --> 22:13.110
you want to use the pocket watch?

22:14.610 --> 22:15.290
I'm sure.

22:18.000 --> 22:19.200
Before we begin,

22:19.350 --> 22:20.550
I want you to remember

22:21.510 --> 22:23.430
that the following experience

22:24.310 --> 22:25.720
will be completely safe.

22:27.160 --> 22:29.310
I need your absolute trust.

22:30.120 --> 22:30.920
You need to

22:31.050 --> 22:32.390
relax your body and mind.

22:32.390 --> 22:33.880
Does hypnosis really work?

22:33.880 --> 22:35.640
Back when Hansheng was working
at the Provincial Bureau,

22:35.640 --> 22:37.050
he solved a kidnapping case.

22:37.050 --> 22:38.340
The eyewitness

22:38.370 --> 22:39.480
had seen the kidnapper's car,

22:39.480 --> 22:41.240
but, due to severe shock,

22:41.310 --> 22:43.240
his memory went completely blank.

22:43.540 --> 22:45.020
We then used

22:45.040 --> 22:46.780
hypnotic investigation methods

22:46.780 --> 22:48.840
to help him recall the whole process,

22:49.050 --> 22:51.470
including the exact license plate numbers.

22:51.470 --> 22:53.330
The case was solved very quickly.

22:54.130 --> 22:55.620
Was it Professor Ding back then too?

22:55.620 --> 22:56.100
Yes.

22:56.390 --> 22:58.110
Professor Ding is my mentor.

22:58.380 --> 22:59.490
He's the nation's

22:59.520 --> 23:01.250
foremost expert in this field.

23:08.400 --> 23:09.330
Jiang Hansheng.

23:12.960 --> 23:14.850
Look at this pocket watch.

23:15.610 --> 23:17.240
Focus completely...

23:18.420 --> 23:19.260
on it.

23:23.370 --> 23:25.290
Take a deep breath in.

23:28.740 --> 23:29.980
Slowly...

23:31.380 --> 23:32.250
let it

23:33.240 --> 23:34.400
out.

23:36.750 --> 23:37.790
Very good.

23:38.950 --> 23:40.840
Your chest is now empty.

23:42.350 --> 23:43.440
Everything...

23:44.570 --> 23:46.530
is very safe.

23:48.850 --> 23:50.360
Everything is relaxed...

23:53.100 --> 23:53.970
and very...

23:55.210 --> 23:56.300
peaceful.

24:09.160 --> 24:10.640
Let's do it again.

24:11.520 --> 24:12.320
Relax.

24:14.690 --> 24:16.620
Take a deep breath.

24:18.030 --> 24:19.140
Gradually...

24:21.130 --> 24:22.610
your eyes

24:23.490 --> 24:25.490
may start to feel heavy.

24:26.770 --> 24:27.720
Very heavy.

24:29.400 --> 24:31.290
You may want to close them.

24:32.440 --> 24:33.640
Now,

24:34.780 --> 24:37.060
just let your body guide you

24:38.420 --> 24:39.870
and close your eyes.

24:58.980 --> 25:00.020
Jiang Hansheng,

25:00.830 --> 25:01.750
we

25:02.240 --> 25:03.680
are back here again—

25:04.510 --> 25:06.550
an empty warehouse.

25:07.720 --> 25:08.810
It's very dark.

25:09.890 --> 25:10.920
It's very dirty.

25:12.330 --> 25:13.260
Jiang Hansheng,

25:13.840 --> 25:15.190
what do you see?

25:15.690 --> 25:17.060
Can you see clearly?

25:18.900 --> 25:20.210
What do you see?

25:20.240 --> 25:20.850
A dead body.

25:20.850 --> 25:22.070
Can you see it clearly?

25:22.070 --> 25:23.640
Whose body is it?

25:23.660 --> 25:24.860
A very young man.

25:24.890 --> 25:26.570
How long has he been dead?

25:28.830 --> 25:30.000
Please let us go!

25:30.000 --> 25:30.880
Please let us go!

25:30.880 --> 25:31.810
Please let us go!

25:32.680 --> 25:33.480
I don't know.

25:34.150 --> 25:35.280
I can't see clearly.

25:35.510 --> 25:37.170
I can't see anything clearly.

25:37.730 --> 25:39.010
No need to rush.

25:39.920 --> 25:41.240
When I

25:41.850 --> 25:43.370
snap my fingers...

25:45.030 --> 25:46.270
you can

25:46.840 --> 25:48.230
relive that time

25:49.480 --> 25:51.890
in this warehouse again—

25:53.930 --> 25:55.660
to experience it all once more.

25:57.510 --> 25:58.440
One.

25:59.680 --> 26:00.960
Your vision

26:01.750 --> 26:04.000
will become clearer...

26:04.430 --> 26:05.990
clearer and clearer.

26:07.420 --> 26:08.010
Two.

26:09.200 --> 26:10.310
Your sensations

26:10.350 --> 26:11.860
will grow stronger

26:11.890 --> 26:13.170
and stronger—

26:13.670 --> 26:14.750
so overwhelming

26:15.050 --> 26:17.980
that you'll feel compelled
to describe everything.

26:19.740 --> 26:20.350
Three!

26:34.470 --> 26:35.270
I can't see.

26:36.150 --> 26:37.350
I can't see anything.

26:37.890 --> 26:39.090
You may not see,

26:39.330 --> 26:40.720
but you can hear.

26:41.270 --> 26:42.480
Listen carefully.

26:43.160 --> 26:44.640
What do you hear?

26:53.240 --> 26:55.300
You ran into me—that's your bad luck!

26:55.640 --> 26:58.120
You saw something you shouldn't have!

27:17.570 --> 27:18.900
There's a woman crying.

27:19.070 --> 27:19.980
Crying?

27:20.560 --> 27:22.320
Besides the crying,

27:23.550 --> 27:24.950
listen carefully again.

27:25.350 --> 27:26.680
What else do you hear?

27:30.310 --> 27:31.070
Let her go!

27:32.220 --> 27:32.640
Stop it!

27:32.640 --> 27:33.500
Don't touch me!

27:33.550 --> 27:34.180
Stop it!

27:34.200 --> 27:34.930
No.

27:36.560 --> 27:37.920
Did I say you could move?

27:47.690 --> 27:48.490
Tell me,

27:49.030 --> 27:50.480
what else did you hear?

27:50.920 --> 27:51.840
Whistling.

28:06.390 --> 28:08.190
You've finally shown yourself.

28:08.400 --> 28:10.130
You cops really are something—

28:10.480 --> 28:12.680
always thinking you can save everyone.

28:12.680 --> 28:13.680
But in reality...

28:16.370 --> 28:18.500
I'll give you a chance, Officer Jiang.

28:18.650 --> 28:20.010
Play a game with me.

28:21.310 --> 28:22.220
Let him down.

28:44.030 --> 28:44.990
Tell me,

28:45.560 --> 28:47.290
what are they doing over there?

28:47.690 --> 28:48.620
Take your time.

29:14.210 --> 29:18.290
[Third day
after Jiang Hansheng was captured]

29:32.360 --> 29:33.620
Carry this over there.

30:23.790 --> 30:24.310
I heard you're

30:24.310 --> 30:27.240
a top graduate
from the Public Security University.

30:28.350 --> 30:29.880
Are you familiar with guns?

30:30.790 --> 30:31.720
What do you want?

30:35.000 --> 30:36.170
A little game.

30:37.920 --> 30:39.030
We'll use...

30:42.640 --> 30:44.300
that oil barrel as the target.

30:44.960 --> 30:46.400
Whoever assembles the gun first

30:46.400 --> 30:48.440
and hits that oil barrel wins.

30:49.070 --> 30:50.030
If you win...

30:51.890 --> 30:53.290
I won't touch that woman.

30:54.880 --> 30:55.610
How about it?

30:59.010 --> 31:01.050
I don't gamble with people's lives.

31:02.940 --> 31:04.160
Please save me. Save me!

31:04.160 --> 31:04.830
No! No!

31:04.830 --> 31:05.510
Please save me!

31:05.510 --> 31:06.110
No! No!

31:06.550 --> 31:07.440
No!

31:08.230 --> 31:08.880
No!

31:09.070 --> 31:09.750
No!

31:10.170 --> 31:10.820
Wait.

31:10.950 --> 31:11.640
Save me.

31:16.190 --> 31:17.320
Break it down again.

31:21.330 --> 31:22.260
What did you say?

31:24.440 --> 31:25.570
Break it down again.

31:51.470 --> 31:52.840
Are you ready?

31:55.790 --> 31:56.440
Begin.

32:14.610 --> 32:15.890
Hurry up. Hurry up.

32:18.560 --> 32:20.080
Faster! Faster!

32:26.380 --> 32:28.060
Lu Xin!

32:33.180 --> 32:33.940
I'm sorry.

32:35.400 --> 32:36.660
I hit the wrong target.

32:38.590 --> 32:39.310
Sorry.

32:40.840 --> 32:42.080
I didn't mean to.

32:43.750 --> 32:44.950
I'm really sorry.

32:44.980 --> 32:46.380
I didn't do it on purpose.

32:49.750 --> 32:50.350
I'm sorry.

32:50.510 --> 32:51.030
I'm sorry.

32:51.030 --> 32:52.030
I'm really sorry.

32:53.990 --> 32:55.470
I truly didn't mean to.

32:55.800 --> 32:56.430
Sorry.

33:26.400 --> 33:28.060
You deliberately provoked me

33:29.050 --> 33:30.310
into coming after you.

33:32.070 --> 33:33.070
Officer Jiang...

33:35.130 --> 33:36.480
Are you challenging me?

33:38.750 --> 33:40.670
Most cops wouldn't act like you.

33:42.870 --> 33:44.200
You're quite unhinged.

33:52.920 --> 33:54.320
Can we pause for a moment?

33:54.480 --> 33:55.420
Hansheng made it clear

33:55.420 --> 33:56.400
that unless it reaches a critical point,

33:56.400 --> 33:57.510
we shouldn't interrupt.

33:57.510 --> 33:58.440
Jiang Hansheng,

33:59.070 --> 33:59.960
don't worry.

34:00.610 --> 34:02.000
You're fine now.

34:02.400 --> 34:03.550
Relax.

34:04.400 --> 34:05.460
Take a deep breath.

34:06.470 --> 34:08.679
Everything is calm now.

34:10.670 --> 34:11.600
Jiang Hansheng,

34:12.659 --> 34:13.860
do you still remember

34:14.630 --> 34:16.030
why we came here?

34:17.020 --> 34:18.580
Can you still see?

34:19.230 --> 34:19.960
Yes, I can.

34:20.510 --> 34:20.960
Good.

34:21.590 --> 34:23.190
Then let's

34:23.290 --> 34:24.810
carefully look over

34:24.920 --> 34:26.920
this entire space once more.

34:27.780 --> 34:28.860
You can

34:29.480 --> 34:31.120
take a look at every corner

34:32.030 --> 34:33.280
and every person.

34:34.750 --> 34:35.310
One.

34:37.400 --> 34:37.960
Two.

34:39.960 --> 34:40.630
Three.

34:42.710 --> 34:43.320
Four.

34:45.230 --> 34:45.920
Tell me.

34:48.420 --> 34:49.969
What are you counting?

34:50.670 --> 34:51.440
One.

34:52.400 --> 34:52.920
Two.

34:54.320 --> 34:54.840
Three.

34:56.360 --> 34:56.920
Four.

34:58.000 --> 34:58.670
Five.

34:59.150 --> 35:00.230
Wasn't it four?

35:02.840 --> 35:03.360
One.

35:05.110 --> 35:05.630
Two.

35:07.150 --> 35:07.760
Three.

35:08.880 --> 35:09.550
Four.

35:11.110 --> 35:11.880
Impossible.

35:13.190 --> 35:13.800
Three.

35:14.840 --> 35:15.510
Four.

35:16.440 --> 35:17.030
Five.

35:18.740 --> 35:19.610
Where is he?

35:22.100 --> 35:23.030
Jiang Hansheng!

35:24.400 --> 35:25.280
Jiang Hansheng,

35:25.280 --> 35:26.110
listen to me.

35:26.570 --> 35:27.650
You're very safe!

35:27.780 --> 35:29.650
You've already been rescued!

35:30.070 --> 35:30.780
Listen carefully—

35:30.780 --> 35:31.770
follow my instructions!

35:31.770 --> 35:33.080
Wake up right now!

35:33.150 --> 35:34.190
Wake up now!

35:40.880 --> 35:41.940
Alright, alright.

35:42.470 --> 35:43.400
You're okay now.

35:46.030 --> 35:47.280
Let's take a break.

35:51.400 --> 35:52.590
Can we go in now?

35:53.330 --> 35:53.890
Yes.

35:58.100 --> 35:58.860
How are you doing?

35:58.860 --> 36:00.000
There weren't four of them.

36:00.000 --> 36:00.570
Are you sure?

36:00.570 --> 36:01.900
I saw five meal boxes

36:02.280 --> 36:03.130
and five pairs of chopsticks.

36:03.130 --> 36:04.740
But all the files you gave me

36:05.070 --> 36:07.000
indicated there were four people.

36:43.080 --> 36:44.340
There were two Qi Yans.

37:11.760 --> 37:12.870
Team 1, in position.

37:12.870 --> 37:14.000
Team 2, in position.

37:14.030 --> 37:15.160
Team 3, in position.

37:15.550 --> 37:16.610
Lock on the target.

37:22.110 --> 37:23.760
The target ship is expected to dock

37:23.760 --> 37:24.820
within 10 minutes.

37:25.030 --> 37:26.030
Once the deal is done,

37:26.030 --> 37:27.030
move in immediately.

37:27.030 --> 37:27.710
Copy that!

37:30.710 --> 37:31.590
Chief Tan,

37:31.610 --> 37:32.730
Professor Jiang is looking for you.

37:32.730 --> 37:34.060
It seems rather urgent.

37:41.190 --> 37:42.630
Director Lu, Commander Liu,

37:42.630 --> 37:44.000
something's come up.
I'll step out for a moment.

37:44.000 --> 37:44.640
Go ahead.

37:44.920 --> 37:45.480
Yes, sir!

37:47.360 --> 37:48.090
Are you sure?

37:48.550 --> 37:49.280
I'm sure.

37:49.920 --> 37:51.510
The man who died five years ago

37:51.510 --> 37:52.310
was not Qi Yan.

37:52.670 --> 37:53.510
And we've just checked with

37:53.510 --> 37:55.550
the forensic examiner
who handled the case at the time.

37:55.550 --> 37:57.030
He said that on Qi Yan's body,

37:57.030 --> 37:58.590
apart from the gunshot wound
between the eyebrows,

37:58.590 --> 37:59.440
there were

37:59.590 --> 38:01.800
no blunt force trauma marks
anywhere on the head.

38:01.800 --> 38:03.330
That doesn't add up either.

38:03.800 --> 38:04.930
Where is Leader Yao?

38:05.040 --> 38:06.840
I haven't been able to reach him.

38:06.920 --> 38:07.920
He's on a mission.

38:08.510 --> 38:10.170
Is it related to the 8/17 Case?

38:14.710 --> 38:17.170
Leader Yao received reliable intelligence

38:17.190 --> 38:18.920
that tonight at Jingang Wharf,

38:19.280 --> 38:21.410
there will be a large-scale drug deal.

38:21.480 --> 38:22.800
The biggest mastermind behind

38:22.800 --> 38:24.460
the 8/17 Case crime syndicate

38:24.670 --> 38:26.470
will be there in person tonight.

38:26.710 --> 38:27.760
So Leader Yao

38:28.030 --> 38:28.900
personally led the team

38:28.900 --> 38:31.000
to Jingang Wharf to carry out the arrest.

38:31.000 --> 38:31.660
It's a trap.

38:32.400 --> 38:33.400
No matter who the source was

38:33.400 --> 38:34.670
or what intel they gave us,

38:34.670 --> 38:36.400
it's highly likely to be a trap.

38:36.880 --> 38:38.800
Why would Leader Yao
personally lead the team?

38:38.800 --> 38:39.760
Could they be using

38:39.760 --> 38:40.670
this so-called mastermind

38:40.670 --> 38:41.930
to lure Leader Yao out?

38:42.510 --> 38:44.230
Qi Yan held significant influence

38:44.230 --> 38:45.480
within the 8/17 Case crime syndicate.

38:45.480 --> 38:46.800
If he's still alive,

38:47.080 --> 38:47.920
he would definitely participate

38:47.920 --> 38:48.810
in such a deal.

38:49.480 --> 38:50.670
Back then, it was Leader Yao

38:50.670 --> 38:52.190
who led the team to arrest them.

38:52.190 --> 38:53.190
It's very likely

38:53.400 --> 38:55.130
a trap they set to get back at us!

38:58.070 --> 38:59.530
The deal is about to start.

39:04.070 --> 39:04.670
Bai Yang!

39:04.840 --> 39:05.370
Yes, sir.

39:06.000 --> 39:07.000
Where is He Wu?

39:07.480 --> 39:09.360
He hasn't moved
since he got to the Ruixiang Hotel.

39:09.360 --> 39:10.550
He's having dinner right now.

39:10.550 --> 39:12.000
Put me through to Leader Yao.

39:12.000 --> 39:13.030
Leader Yao, Leader Yao,

39:13.030 --> 39:14.160
this is Tan Shiming.

39:14.190 --> 39:15.030
What's going on?

39:15.030 --> 39:16.490
There are a lot of unknowns

39:16.550 --> 39:17.950
in tonight's operation.

39:18.230 --> 39:19.320
Listen to me,

39:19.710 --> 39:20.670
Qi Yan...

39:21.800 --> 39:22.800
might not be dead.

39:23.260 --> 39:24.690
He's very likely to appear at

39:24.690 --> 39:25.820
tonight's deal.

39:26.150 --> 39:27.710
Qi Yan is still alive?

39:27.880 --> 39:29.480
I don't have time to explain.

39:29.710 --> 39:30.400
In short,

39:30.760 --> 39:31.980
Professor Jiang's analysis suggests

39:31.980 --> 39:34.910
that the person
who died five years ago wasn't Qi Yan.

39:35.000 --> 39:36.230
Tonight's deal

39:36.400 --> 39:38.070
is likely a trap set by him.

39:38.280 --> 39:39.400
So far,

39:39.400 --> 39:40.840
He Wu hasn't arrived at the wharf.

39:40.840 --> 39:42.700
That alone is highly suspicious.

39:47.840 --> 39:49.570
Chief Tan, the boat has docked.

39:54.760 --> 39:55.440
Leader Yao!

39:56.840 --> 39:58.880
Compared to the deal,

39:58.920 --> 40:00.710
Qi Yan is more interested in the police.

40:00.710 --> 40:02.480
Professor Jiang analyzed it the same way.

40:02.480 --> 40:05.080
Do we still proceed with
tonight's operation?

40:10.990 --> 40:12.190
It's been five years.

40:12.390 --> 40:14.380
We've finally mapped out

40:14.480 --> 40:15.880
the entire Jin-Hai Line.

40:16.650 --> 40:19.310
Old Scorpion has been in hiding
all these years,

40:19.440 --> 40:21.400
and now he's finally showing himself.

40:21.400 --> 40:22.030
Yes.

40:23.480 --> 40:24.960
This is our only chance.

40:27.280 --> 40:28.190
When it's over,

40:28.500 --> 40:29.620
I can go home.

40:33.590 --> 40:35.000
I understand the situation.

40:35.000 --> 40:36.400
Send two more police units

40:36.400 --> 40:37.730
to the wharf for backup.

40:38.000 --> 40:39.120
Let's proceed as planned.

40:39.120 --> 40:39.760
Copy that.

40:44.590 --> 40:46.030
According to informants,

40:46.030 --> 40:48.480
the target ship docking at Jingang Wharf

40:48.590 --> 40:50.360
is carrying a large quantity of drugs.

40:50.360 --> 40:51.960
The buyer coming for the deal

40:52.070 --> 40:53.550
is a criminal syndicate
that has been hiding

40:53.550 --> 40:55.350
in the Jin-Hai region for years.

40:55.590 --> 40:56.550
Their leader

40:57.280 --> 40:58.710
is the drug kingpin our police

40:58.710 --> 41:00.640
have been pursuing for a long time—

41:01.070 --> 41:02.070
known by the alias

41:02.440 --> 41:03.240
Old Scorpion.

41:03.360 --> 41:04.620
His specific identity

41:05.070 --> 41:06.510
and physical features are unknown.

41:06.510 --> 41:07.970
We only know his nickname.

41:08.070 --> 41:09.800
Proceed with extreme caution.

41:10.810 --> 41:11.560
Leaders,

41:11.900 --> 41:13.260
I'm heading to the scene immediately.

41:13.260 --> 41:13.890
Go ahead.

41:13.920 --> 41:14.740
Leave this to us.

41:14.740 --> 41:15.270
Yes, sir!

41:20.750 --> 41:22.150
Senior, why are you here?

41:22.630 --> 41:23.690
Same reason as you.

41:40.150 --> 41:41.110
Don't stop me.

41:41.590 --> 41:42.550
Trust me,

41:43.000 --> 41:43.670
okay?

42:01.880 --> 42:02.840
Be careful.

42:17.200 --> 42:18.190
Keep your eyes on the target

42:18.190 --> 42:18.960
and report immediately.

42:18.960 --> 42:19.940
Do not act alone...

42:19.940 --> 42:21.110
Senior, which car should I be in?

42:21.110 --> 42:22.510
Junior, why are you here?

42:25.000 --> 42:26.330
What are you doing here?

42:26.400 --> 42:27.480
Who told you to come?

42:27.480 --> 42:28.110
Sir,

42:28.310 --> 42:29.710
Officer Zhou Jin requests
to join the operation.

42:29.710 --> 42:30.640
Stay out of this.

42:30.670 --> 42:31.320
Sir,

42:31.480 --> 42:33.150
Officer Zhou Jin requests
to join the operation!

42:33.150 --> 42:35.140
I've been waiting for this day
for five years.

42:35.140 --> 42:36.470
Please grant approval.

42:37.920 --> 42:38.440
Mentor,

42:38.440 --> 42:41.370
if you really can't stop her,
just let her come along.

42:41.840 --> 42:42.700
How about this?

42:43.030 --> 42:44.110
You'll go with the team tracking He Wu.

42:44.110 --> 42:44.730
Mentor!

42:44.750 --> 42:46.030
Don't say I didn't give you a chance.

42:46.030 --> 42:48.510
And don't say
I didn't give you an assignment!

42:48.510 --> 42:49.400
Are you all ready?

42:49.400 --> 42:50.070
Ready.

42:50.070 --> 42:50.870
Then move out!

42:51.420 --> 42:51.920
Junior,

42:51.940 --> 42:53.470
you go with Zhao Ping's car.

42:53.510 --> 42:54.150
Be good.

43:02.150 --> 43:02.800
Zhao Ping,

43:02.800 --> 43:03.480
stop the car!

43:03.480 --> 43:04.110
Senior.

43:04.110 --> 43:04.760
Let me in!

43:04.760 --> 43:05.240
Get in.
